OL,3,CTrial date set for detective charged
OL,4,Cwith upskirting a teenage girl
OL,6,FA trial date has been set for a 45-
OL,7,Fyear-old former North Wales Police
OL,8,Fdetective who has been charged with
OL,9,Fupskirting a teenage girl.
OL,11,FDetective Constable Lee Harshey-Jones,
OL,12,Fof Francis Avenue in Conwy, appeared
OL,13,Fat Chester Crown Court on Tuesday (14
OL,14,FJuly) for a plea and trial preparation
OL,15,Fhearing.
OL,17,FNo pleas were entered, but a
OL,18,Fprovisional trial date was set for
OL,19,FAugust 16 2027 which is scheduled for
OL,20,Ffive days.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
