OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784139506
OL,3,CTrial date set for detective charged
OL,4,Cwith upskirting a teenage girl
OL,6,FJudge Michael Leeming also granted him
OL,7,Fconditional bail.
OL,9,FMr Harshey-Jones was arrested
OL,10,Ffollowing an incident in the Colwyn
OL,11,FBay area last month and was later
OL,12,Fsuspended by his employers North Wales
OL,13,FPolice.
OL,15,FThe former detective has been charged
OL,16,Fwith recording an image under clothing
OL,17,Fto observe another without consent,
OL,18,Fknown as "upskirting".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
