OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784139506
OL,3,CTrial date set for detective charged
OL,4,Cwith upskirting a teenage girl
OL,6,FHe is also charged with perverting the
OL,7,Fcourse of justice and improper use of
OL,8,Fpolice powers and privileges.
OL,10,FOperating equipment beneath clothing
OL,11,Fwithout consent is an offence under
OL,12,Fthe Sexual Offences Act 2003
OL,14,FMr Harshey-Jones was the lead
OL,15,Finvestigator in the death of two-year-
OL,16,Fold Ethan Ives-Griffiths, who was
OL,17,Fmurdered by his grandparents in 2021.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
