OL,3,CTrial date set for detective charged
OL,4,Cwith upskirting a teenage girl
OL,6,FNorth Wales Police has said the
OL,7,Fofficer had been suspended from
OL,8,Fduties. A spokesperson also added it
OL,9,Fwould be inappropriate for the force
OL,10,Fto comment further on the matter at
OL,11,Fthis time.
